{"tid":266292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警上門查偷拍裙底案 男子墮樓 身體斷成兩截","createTime":"2017-06-01T10:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T05:38:54.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2d708947bc3b15788b71e44f80ec754b8a45219","tid":266292,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:54:48.000Z","msg":"沙田發生離奇墮樓案，下午4時許，一名男子由翠田街愉景花園一單位高處墮下，當場慘死，身體斷成兩截，死狀恐怖。消息指出，上周四(25日)一名女子報稱在辦公室內疑遭人偷拍裙底，黃大仙警區刑事調查隊今午到愉景花園一單位調查，其間警員尚未入屋，一名男子突然墮樓身亡。警方事後撿獲遺書，正調查案件原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91441b9fc70a103b9d1b60339ffdbe26b142a6a2","tid":266292,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"36593c8df3605f50ce809c6f8281630f28f03c33","tid":266292,"uid":97634,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會係連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b898ae30b69250d433b39b47717290f9bc604c79","tid":266292,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"有冇睇字 個肚都不自覺緊緊收縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c705022c630a52424dce39a8335627f4540444fe","tid":266292,"uid":8394,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"警員未入屋？<br />\n邊個知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94542cf46c50f172edeab2c002d399f05cf0ff99","tid":266292,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"又係東九wor ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b270ec7f82ca6809cea7db568dbb73f395a666b","tid":266292,"uid":36178,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"情願跳樓斷兩截都唔比黑警用lan線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e67884e1b0ab5e